- Stop it.

229
00:18:41,833 --> 00:18:44,583
- Enough! Calm down, Thusnelda.
- What are you doing?

230
00:18:44,666 --> 00:18:46,041
- Don't!
- Not now.

231
00:18:54,125 --> 00:18:57,291
- Let go of me!
- Hold him down!

232
