236
00:19:27,041 --> 00:19:28,833
Rome victorious!

237
00:19:33,416 --> 00:19:35,500
No, no, no, no...

238
00:19:39,458 --> 00:19:40,458
Please!

239
00:20:31,666 --> 00:20:35,166
