I didn't want this to happen.

240
00:20:59,166 --> 00:21:00,625
Women of the woods...

241
00:21:03,166 --> 00:21:04,375
take my sacrifice.

242
00:21:20,416 --> 00:21:21,833
Mother of Blood...

243
00:21:23,041 --> 00:21:24,375
