251
00:21:51,708 --> 00:21:53,208
death and doom.

252
00:21:56,125 --> 00:21:57,750
And be a good sister to me now...

253
00:21:59,416 --> 00:22:00,916
though I was not.

254
00:22:03,166 --> 00:22:04,750
Though I was not.

255
00:22:30,875 --> 00:22:36,541
